\c 25
\s Bhiridhadhi anorumbidza ukuru hwaMwari
\p
\v 1 Zvino Bhiridhadhi muShuhi wakapindura ndokuti:
\p
\v 2 Utongi nekutyisa zvinaye; achiita rugare panzvimbo dzake dzakakwirira.
\v 3 Kune uwandu here kuhondo dzake? Ndiani kusingabudiri kwaari chiedza chake?
\v 4 Zvino munhu angava wakarurama sei kuna Mwari? Kana wakaberekwa nemukadzi angachena sei?
\v 5 Tarira, nomwedziwo unoshaiwa kubhinya, nenyeredzi hadzizakachena kwazvo pamberi pake.
\v 6 Ndoda munhu, iro gonye! Nomwanakomana womunhu, iro gonye!